**#CyberPatriot Battle Plan**

**##Windows 10 /Windows Server Battle Plan**

1. Create restore point
2. Enable Firewall / Defender
2. Configure Defender AV for weekly scheduled scans
3. Configure AppLocker
4. Run Windows update
  Open a admin powershell session
  type Install-Module PSWindowsUpdate
  This will install the Windows Update module for Windows Powershell.
  type Get-WindowsUpdate
  This will connect to the Windows Update servers and download the updates if found.
  type Install-WindowsUpdate
  close powershell
5. Create an audit policy WINDOWS ADVANCED LOGGING CHEAT SHEET 
6. Answer Forensic questions
7. Reboot
8. Run a system audit tool, MS Compliance Toolkit  MS SCT HowTo 
   Correct problems found in audit tool

**##Ubuntu Linux CyberPatriot Battle Plan**

1. Enable GUFW Firewall
2. Enable ClamAV
3. Install auditd and create audit rules
4. Enable Apparmor
5. OS Update   terminal: sudo apt-get update
6. Answer Foresic questions
7. Reboot
8. Follow Best Practices Guide
9. Run a system audit tool, Lynis
10. Correct problems found in audit tool
